column2: # Question 1: Build Cumulative logit model with Job~ Gender + Income
cbind(`Very Dissatisfied`,`A Little Satisfied`,`Moderately Satisfied`,`Very Satisfied`) ~ factor(Income) + factor(Gender == 'Female'),

vglm(formula = cbind(`Very Dissatisfied`, `A Little Satisfied`, 
    `Moderately Satisfied`, `Very Satisfied`) ~ factor(Income) + 
    factor(Gender == "Female"), family = cumulative(parallel = TRUE), 
    data = job_df)
No Hauck-Donner effect found in any of the estimates
